{"tid":1977730,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"原來香港恐怖份子: 狗賊曾經要求Google移除狗賊既訓練守則、狗賊姓名同資料、匿名者撐手足片段同hkmap.live","createTime":"2020-04-18T07:33:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T02:48:57.000Z","uid":51271,"like":437,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":91,"replies":[{"pid":"8d202530f4038c562ee17a38765e874a46fdf5a2","tid":1977730,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:33:09.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但Google全部都無應恐怖份子無理要求</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港<br />\n要求<br />\n<br />\nThe Hong Kong Police requested we remove a publicly shared Drive PDF file that contained &quot;The Book of Secrets&quot;, a 171-page confidential training procedure manual used by the Hong Kong police. They claimed that the content might have contravened section 161 of Crimes Ordinance &ndash; Access to computer with dishonest intent.<br />\n結果<br />\n<br />\nWe did not remove and asked the police to provide more information.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港<br />\n要求<br />\n<br />\nThe Privacy Commissioner requested we delist a URL from Google Search on data protection grounds. The site permitted users to look up information about police officers by name or officer identity number. They claimed that the site contravened section 64 of the Personal Data (Privacy) Ordinance and Data Protection Principle 3.<br />\n結果<br />\n<br />\nWe did not delist the URL.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港<br />\n要求<br />\n<br />\nWe received a request from the Hong Kong police to remove a YouTube video uploaded by Anonymous, a decentralized hacktivist group that is widely known for their cyber attacks. In the video, Anonymous commented on the Hong Kong protests, calling for protesters to remain vigilant.<br />\n結果<br />\n<br />\nWe did not remove the video.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港<br />\n要求<br />\n<br />\nThe Hong Kong police requested we remove an app that enabled users to share the locations of police and protesters from Google Play Store. The police claimed that the app was in violation of Section 90 - Penalties for assisting offenders of Cap. 211 Criminal Procedure Ordinance.<br />\n結果<br />\n<br />\nWe did not remove the app.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://transparencyreport.google.com/government-removals/by-country/HK?country_request_explore=period:;authority:HK&amp;lu=country_request_explore\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftransparencyreport.google.com%2Fgovernment-removals%2Fby-country%2FHK%3Fcountry_request_explore%3Dperiod%3A%3Bauthority%3AHK%26lu%3Dcountry_request_explore&d=0xR7vGHOl893LUq1yoppegOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=4f19665a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://transparencyreport.google.com/government-removals/by-country/HK?country_request_explore=period:;authority:HK&amp;lu=country_request_explore</a>"},{"pid":"8a1a44fb1453c64902b2ecd4249e066a23a847a7","tid":1977730,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:35:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c049506613b0f1ed5b8aa9fa81e17b21fdacc8d","tid":1977730,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:35:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a436754532f97b5a5726897edad55ea34000e532","tid":1977730,"uid":66221,"like":61,"dislike":1,"score":60,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:35:09.000Z","msg":"我唔知啦，但其實係咪只係個權係美國根本越唔到權所以先唔應承？"},{"pid":"d5fb35144ccf4272a3a342c743a53fddaebbd7f2","tid":1977730,"uid":89349,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:35:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200418/large/1587141530_0e44.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200418%2Flarge%2F1587141530_0e44.jpg&h=5e1f1c81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br