995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0afd5f780529047e1e4f4a277ff6682214d94030","tid":1977730,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"185309179aac0a600d77c1efd054edf85aef8bc1","tid":1977730,"uid":11454,"like":57,"dislike":1,"score":56,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T08:03:46.000Z","msg":"所以香港人要面對現實, 唔止黑警想殺你, 係成個香港政府, 無時無刻都想搞你, 搞到你死為止<br />\n手執行政, 執法權利就用到盡, 每一件小事, 只要搵到位就會拉你, 告你<br />\n只有香港獨立, 推翻成個政府先算嬴"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T08:09:57.000Z","msg":"係，講得非常正確"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T08:21:09.000Z","msg":"用手機拍攝張20蚊銀紙都犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根本就求其作個理由出黎"},{"pid":"5668d65a921c7d652d447b436990b479e0e53d9a","tid":1977730,"uid":236003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T08:22:02.000Z","msg":"好撚惡，幾時揮軍去打鳩google總公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da50aa2b95ccc26af2c732bbbcc524a9aae7c9de","tid":1977730,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6d4ac3067c367bc517b4936d2605b3b786966900","tid":1977730,"uid":126510,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T08:17:10.000Z","msg":"禁埋去睇 中國對Google嘅request 都幾精彩<br />\n<br />\n原來Google keep d咁嘅嘢<br />\n正"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T08:23:55.000Z","msg":"中國<br />\n要求<br />\n<br />\nWe received a removal request from the China Internet Illegal Information Reporting Center (CIIIRC) under Article 12 of the Cybersecurity Law. The issue related to the listing of the Hong Kong Liaison Office being searchable under an allegedly insulting name.<br />\n結果<br />\n<br />\nThe issue was fixed per Google Maps product policy.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n邊個手足幫屎忽幫改名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f567a8863613167aa7f0ef3c8b76a9d4f184b58d","tid":1977730,"uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T08:24:44.000Z","msg":"中國<br />\n要求<br />\n<br />\nWe received 96 requests from the Ministry of Public Security of China to remove 1352 YouTube URLs allegedly featuring content related to the East Turkestan Islamic Movement (ETIM). The majority of the URLs were documentary or news footage from the media.<br />\n結果<br />\n<br />\nWe removed 30 URLs for violating YouTube Community Guidelines and age-restricted 435 URLs for depicting graphic or violent scenes. We did not remove the remaining 887 URLs.<br />\n中國<br />\n要求<br />\n<br />\n我們收到中國公安部 (Ministry of Public Security) 和國家互聯網信息辦公室 (Cyberspace Administration) 提出的 127 項要求，希望我們審查 1601 個 YouTube 影片網址 (大多是重複的影片)。這些影片的內容絕大部分都與東突厥斯坦伊斯蘭運動 (East Turkestan Islamic Movement，ETIM) 有關，其他影片則是與仇恨言論相關的內容和涉嫌批評政府。<br />\n結果<br />\n<br />\n我們依據《YouTube 社群規範》對其中 4 部影片設下年齡限制，並終止了其中 2 部影片所屬的頻道，但並未對剩下的 1595 個網址採取任何行動。<br />\n中國<br />\n要求<br />\n<br />\n我們收到中國公安部 (Ministry of Public Security) 提出的要求，希望我們從幾項產品中移除與東突厥斯坦伊斯蘭運動 (East Turkestan Islamic Movement) 有關的內容。<br />\n結果<br />\n<br />\n我們移除了 4 個雲端硬碟檔案、2 則 Google+ 訊息和 1 個 Google+ 個人資料，因為這些內容違反了產品政策中禁止暴力極端主義內容的相關規定。<br />\n中國<br />\n要求<br />\n<br />\n我們收到中國公安部 (Ministry of Public Security) 提出的 199 項要求，指出共有 412 部 YouTube 影片和 7 個 YouTube 頻道違反誹謗、隱私權、仇恨言論、暴力和暴力極端主義的規定。其中的 346 部影片含有指控中華人民共和國政治體系內存在貪汙情事，或與政府高級官員有關的傳言內容。其他 66 部影片和 7 個頻道則遭指稱與東突厥斯坦伊斯蘭運動 (East Turkestan Islamic Movement，ETIM) 有關，因此希望我們移除這些內容。<br />\n結果<br />\n<br />\n我們依據《YouTube 社群規範》移除了 257 部影片，並對 2 部影片設下年齡限制。我們也終止了 3 個與極端主義團體有關的頻道。我們並未移除剩下的 153 個網址及另外 4 個頻道。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我好相信港共好快會用同一招對付反送中"},{"pid":"00991a9388bc2e515e2af5def0919964d8e0ebda","tid":1977730,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T08:28:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"312eb5aeab2f2cc2e49508ce9d4cb46106a